    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>Vaidy is a kernel developer at <span class="caps">IBM</span> Linux Technology Center.  He has been working on improving energy efficiency of Linux running on enterprise hardware including Linux on <span class="caps">IBM</span> <span class="caps">POWER</span> platforms by exploiting platform power saving features and improve efficiency.</p>
